    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A Malorian Arms market survey in 2043 revealed a gap in the average consumer's arsenal which they eagerly stepped in to exploit - a cheap, reliable, effective way to get a lot of mass downrange very quickly, without necessarily devastating its surroundings in the process. And thus, the harpoon cannon was born.</p><p>The Malorian Arms Harpoon Cannon is an exotic grenade launcher which is fired using the heavy weapons skill, but which uses the Handgun DV table. Using a combination of compressed air and magnetic propulsion, it fires proprietary Malorian harpoons which function as armor-piercing ammunition, and which can be retrieved for reuse once fired. Requires BODY 8 to be used effectively.</p><p>The cannon also works underwater!</p>"
